            <h2>Hi, I'm Chas.</h2>
            <p>I'm the founder of Aptible. I'm a developer and enterpreneur with a background in regulatory law. I live and work in Washington, DC.</p>
            <p>I want to build technology that helps people lead healthy, happy lives.</p>
            <p>I'm especially interested in making it easier for cloud-based software developers to comply with health IT regulations.</p>
            <p>I blog <a href="http://chasballew.tumblr.com" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
