        <div class="span4" id="current">
            <h2>Current projects:</h2>
            <p>I want to make it easier for people to gather and analyze data about their health. I also want to make it easier for healthcare providers to help patients outside of acute and ambulatory care settings.</p>
            <p>I'm working on an SMS campaign platform for health interventions. Providers would be able to use the platorm to run clinically-validated programs for 
                <a href="http://jamia.bmj.com/content/early/2012/04/12/amiajnl-2011-000748.abstract" target="_blank">medication adherence</a>, 
                <a href="http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2261/12/36" target="_blank">cardiac rehab</a>, 
                <a href="http://www.ajmc.com/articles/Care-by-Cell-Phone-Text-Messaging-for-Chronic-Disease-Management" target="_blank">chronic disease management</a>, 
                <a href="http://mobihealthnews.com/18822/center-for-connected-health-to-study-sms-for-managing-cancer-pain/" target="_blank">pain management</a>, 
                <a href="http://www.ihealthbeat.org/articles/2013/5/3/study-text-messages-improve-outcomes-for-children-with-asthma.aspx" target="_blank">asthma monitoring</a>, 
                <a href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD006611.pub3/abstract;jsessionid=045CC4FE821F9763C9909D05AD7AFBE3.d03t01" target="_blank">smoking cessation</a>, etc. Researchers would be able to use the platform to develop new studies on the efficacy of SMS interventions.</p>
            <hr class="visible-phone">
